org.drip.calc.output
Class BasketOutput

java.lang.Object
  org.drip.analytics.core.Serializer
      org.drip.calc.output.BasketOutput

public class BasketOutput
extends Serializer

This class has the place holder for the analytical basket measures, optionally across scenarios. Contains measure maps for unadjusted base IR/credit curves, flat delta/gamma bump measure maps for IR/credit bump curves, component/tenor bump double maps for IR/credit curves, flat/component recovery bumped measure maps for recovery bumped credit curves
